review: On having serious teeth pain my friend recommended that I should visit Dr Sanjay Muhury of Relief and care dental clinic.I visited the clinic,the behaviour of dentist and the ambience assured me that I came to right place.After an x ray  performed by him in the clinic he detected that I have a serious infection in my gum and teeth.His expert treatment and proper care healed my teeth problem completely.The state of the art equipments along with expert care of Dr Muhury makes this clinic an unique place for dental treatment and solution.I strongly recommend everyone to visit here for dental care,hygiene and solutions as I learned one thing for sure proper care and awareness saves a lot of trouble.
reply_text: Thank you mr sam for your briiliant feedback ..we are very happy for your satisfaction..whenever come to india plz visit again..

tags: Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review:
I had an intrinsic pain in my left gums , ears which spreaded till my eyes and head resulting in massive pain ,which seemed to be unknown pain to me.
Dr. Sanjay investigated it further and found infectious gum in my molar along with cavity in the same. I underwent a gum surgery and still underway in his treatment. 
I must say, I did not feel a bit of pain during the surgery and currently during the post surgery, pain is also bearable. I would definitely recommend him for any kind of dental procedures since my entire family is under his treatment and we are extremely satisfied with the "relief and care" he provides.
reply_text: Thank you so much debadrita for your brilliant feedback and reviews you shared in the forum..hope for more smile in upcoming future !!..take care..
